ologies\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the support of state funding secured by SenatorHenry Sternand AssemblymemberJesse Gabrielfor the TTIZ, LACI will work in collaboration with SupervisorLindsey Horvath, Councilmember Bob Blumenfield, the Warner Center Association, and LACI's TEP members to issue and seek zero emission technology solutions that can be deployed in service of the community's needs.\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 5084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4825, \"end\": 4829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder_of_Laci_Peterson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LACI\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder_of_Laci_Peterson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murder_of_Laci_Peterson\"}, {\"begin\": 4924, \"end\": 4930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"score\": 0.9999777888935721, \"rank\": 2.221067739484475e-05, \"text\": \"Warner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 4722, \"to\": 4733}, {\"ngram\": \"state funding\", \"from\": 4737, \"to\": 4750}, {\"ngram\": \"SenatorHenry Sternand AssemblymemberJesse\", \"from\": 4762, \"to\": 4803}, {\"ngram\": \"the TTIZ\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4823}, {\"ngram\": \"collaboration\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"SupervisorLindsey Horvath\", \"from\": 4862, \"to\": 4887}, {\"ngram\": \"zero emission technology solutions\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5026}, {\"ngram\": \"service\", \"from\": 5051, \"to\": 5058}, {\"ngram\": \"the community's needs\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first priority will be an electric on-demand micro-transit shuttle in a pilot to explore meeting the needs of the Warner Center community.\", \"from\": 5085, \"to\": 5227, \"e